snippet.title: Irrelevance V - A Connor Sherlock "Walking Simulator"
snippet.description:
Explore Neptune's largest moon, Triton.

This is the fourth of Connor Sherlock's monthly releases, having previously played Birthplace of Ossian. They're weirdly engrossing, atmospheric, and are pretty terrible for YouTube audiences, so I'm really looking forward to them!

You can get this and future works of Connor Sherlock at his Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/connorsherlock

• SUBSCRIBE: http://goo.gl/E3y5FX
Patreon: http://patreon.com/kurtjmac
Twitter: http://twitter.com/kurtjmac
Livestream: http://twitch.tv/kurtjmac

Thanks for watching! Like, favorite, subscribe, whatnot, indeed, and etcetera!
